name: #MANEQ - Interstice
description:
How I miss sinking into your bright eyes.

-----

2592 × 4608, 240px
Shoot on Olympus E PL-5, CCTV Lens.

-----

#Maneq is a series of works that explore emotions through a bland body. Using mannequins as a medium, this work cultivates the honesty of the body that no longer needs to rely on facial expressions. Besides, our faces are just masks, isn't it?
